{"tid":2129912,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"留學移民/香港就業一問","createTime":"2020-07-29T02:38:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-10T18:18:38.000Z","uid":192225,"like":22,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"152809421c0041da0e92472923a0d287e15ad8d6","tid":2129912,"uid":192225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T02:38:45.000Z","msg":"講返少少背景先，小弟係三大讀緊n展，嚟緊fall sem就year 4。由於小弟對香港既未來並唔樂觀，所以都想移民做二等公民，但係有個問題就係，到底我應該畢咗業就直接去外國讀多個master做留學移民定係留係香港做幾年野先去外國移民。<br />\n<br />\n至於地方方面，小弟依家有兩個地方，一係英國，一係加拿大。想去英國既原因係因為去過英國exchange，對英國都幾有好感，加上英國可以去ICE考牌，雖然屋企人有BNO，但係佢地都好似唔想咁快去新地方重新開始咁。而我見加拿大做留學移民就比較易，只要讀完master有人請就可以留底搞移民，但係我就對加拿大既engine一啲頭緒都無，一啲都唔識。有冇過來人或者連登大神指教下小弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n小弟第一次開po，不喜勿插<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />sorry for 1999<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />直接留學移民<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />做返幾年野先"},{"pid":"d496eff652545d7fe39cb8b193d7516412d201ae","tid":2129912,"uid":192225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T02:39:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"14409cd8bbb6d12c20752687491358b3dfa1477f","tid":2129912,"uid":225871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T02:44:44.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"70e5747e56f41534be18e14bb9da720e1aceac62","tid":2129912,"uid":54946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T02:46:06.000Z","msg":"有冇野心，想唔想搵多啲錢。 定你為求work life balance<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"557d71bb856defdfb4edb5f92469a585a98bfed8","tid":2129912,"uid":35420,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T02:46:11.000Z","msg":"讀完master有人請就可以留底搞移民<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有人請先算<br />\n唔到你簡"},{"pid":"859bd2c0e8ddc405cfd7b3cd10d9da23454f93c3","tid":2129912,"uid":192225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"70e5747e56f4153